{"tid":1811915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"背囊品牌Fjällräven接投訴 為台灣「去中國」正名","createTime":"2020-01-05T06:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T11:18:58.000Z","uid":178875,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e118636b9a582eb96704e5de65de652d876f04a","tid":1811915,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wMxbYy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wMxbYy.jpg&h=175f0318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國大陸肆意打壓台灣國際生存空間，在「一個中國」原則下，不少跨國商業機構及國際品牌，都被迫將台灣列作「中國台灣」（Taiwan, China）。在香港擁有不少擁躉的瑞典背囊品牌Fj&auml;llr&auml;ven（北極狐），早前舉行2020年極地滑雪活動大使選舉，有台灣人發現Fj&auml;llr&auml;ven將台灣寫成「Taiwan, China」，隨即去信要求修正，最後獲該公司正面回應，並改回「Taiwan」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67XcWrf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67XcWrf.png&h=61655b26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FGpNx2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FGpNx2.png&h=d066f3e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91UqjM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91UqjM.png&h=5e599a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDLmPMu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDLmPMu.png&h=3343b1b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200104/60450339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F60450339&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLd5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=ba284018\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200104%2F60450339&h=1fd04343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200104/60450339</a>"},{"pid":"739009c96c450590429c5278427542ae5620b9cc","t